# 🩺 Health Census Web Application

A simple web application to collect and display health census data using JavaScript DOM manipulation.

## 🚀 Live Demo

https://mcchiquito.github.io/heath_census/

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (DOM Manipulation)

## 📚 Features

* Dynamic form data handling
* Input validation
* Real-time DOM updates
* Data visualization using tables
* Responsive layout

## 🎯 What I Learned

* Handling user input with JavaScript
* Updating the DOM dynamically
* Structuring responsive layouts
* Managing simple data workflows in frontend applications
* Deploying projects using GitHub Pages

